# OCR Service Enhanced ‚Äî National ID Verification

Hardened Iranian national ID card OCR using LangChain + GPT-4o with anti-forgery validation.

## Files

```
project-root/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ocr_service_enhanced.py   # Main module with both functions
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ examples/                 # Few-shot example images (required)
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ authentic_card_1.jpg
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ authentic_card_2.jpg
